FBIS4-16279 "drsov073_s_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 Georgia Abkhazian `Mercenaries' Actions Reported Abkhazian `Mercenaries' Actions Reported LD1404164994 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY in Russian 1445 GMT 14 Apr 94 LD1404164994 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY Russian BFN [Text] It became known that on 11 and 12 April, Abkhazian separatists and mercenaries looted and burned down about 25 dwelling houses in the village of Pichora in Gali Rayon. Several defenseless elderly people were brutally killed. The unrestrained actions of Abkhazian militants has reached its peak while negotiations on a peaceful settlement of the conflict are under way. The Gudauta grouping has no power to control criminal activities of hired murderers and looters.
